asm3model

This distribution contains compiled Python extension modules derived from the "ASM3 model" implementation within the BSM1 platform.

The upstream DTU/LU agreement provided by the user is reproduced below as the governing upstream notice for the underlying model implementation.

Source of upstream agreement:
"ASM1, 2d & 3 module within BSM1 — Agreement with Technical University of Denmark (DTU), Lund University (LU), Nov 2015"

